  "synopsis": "**One of the Greatest Jedi Must Stop an Explosive Secret From Falling Into the Wrong Hands!**\n\nOn the refinery moon Ro Mira, Mace Windu and smuggler Azita Cruuz, carrying the formula to a paradigm-smashing energy source, are on the run from Ro Mira's security forces and a Hutt-hired bounty hunter. Can Mace dispatch a squadron of fighters led by the ruthless Anzellan Yaya Shram with nothing by his lightsaber and the Force? Introducing Muro and Diya, Dusk Weavers of the Had'le Path, a cult obsessed with wiping technology from the face of the galaxy!",
